Shugaban kasar Indiya zai halarci bikin kafa titin gidan gaskiya a wani wurin makamarwa
NEW DELHI (AP) - Shugaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya na Indiya, Narendra Modi, zai yiwa wani jami'in wanda Hindu ke gina jami'a a wani wurinsa na yammacin Indiya adadi mai zafi a watan Afrilu na shekarar 1996 da majami'u Hindu sun kwashe, shi ne a cikin alamun kula da ginin jami'a.
Tarhon kara ne a shirye a ranar 5 ga watan Agusta, wani lokaci mai albarka da masu shaida suka ce ga majalisa Hindu din, amma kuma wani shekara da suke nan da za su yi sanadiyyar kulla al'adun jihohi marar Musulmai a tsakanin jihohar Indiya, Jammu da Kashmir.
Symbololiyarmu bai wucewa ga masu goyon bayan da kuma yankeewa da kansu na cikakken taaziyar Hindu na Jam'iyyar Jama'a ta Bharatiya Janata, ko BJP, wanda jakata da daya ce tun farko ya yada alwashin rakaitawa kasa na Kamsarol ta Kashmir makiyaya da kuma gina babban daki na ubangijin Hindu daga inda Masallacin zaman Mulgal da daya kafin nan a birnin Ayodhya a jihar Uttar Pradesh, inda masu biyayya ke zaton daga baya cewa, nan ne wurin haihuwa na Ram.
Saboda coronavirus din karye ne a jere a kan Indiya, wanda ta ruwaito tagomacin gwajiya na uku a duniya, bikin zai kwararowa cikin talabijin na gwamnati, kuma babban yarjejeniyar karya da ma'aikatar ya kamata, kamar yadda Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko Hukumar Hindu na Duniya, kungiyar Hindu mai tau'e ya shaida, yaki da BJP.
Dakin akan yi aiki kamar "tsakiyar tsabar karkashin zaman lafiya, haɗin kan kasar da integrasiyar kuma sanzaƙiye na kamar yadda Hindu," ko hanyar rayuwa ta Hindu, mai magana da yawun kasa na kungiyar Vinod Bansal ya ce a cikin sanarwar labarai ta Asabar.
