Bayanin UN yace da dubu masu huldar Pakistan ke a Afghanistan
ISLAMABAD -- Wani rahoton U.N. yace fiye da mutane 6,000 da suka saba ce wadanda suke damuna ‘yan Afghanistan, yawancin su ma’anar Jama’ar Taliban wadda ta shiga haram a Pakistan, wadanda suke kai hare-haren suka kai ta'addan jirgi da rayuwar ‘yan kasa da makamancin Pakistan.
Rahoton da aka saki wannan makon ya ce, kungiyar da ake saninta da suna Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP) ta hadu da kungiyar Islamic State ta mulkin Afghanistan.
Wasu daga cikin 'yan takiyar TTP sun shiga ma'aikatan IS da ke da ma'aikata a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afghan bai amsa tambayoyin daga Associated Press a ranar Lahadi ba.
Rahoton ya ce IS a Afghanistan, wanda ake kira IS a jihar Khorasan, ya sha rikice-rikice daga hanyoyin tsaro na Afghanistan da ma'ajiyar Amurka da NATO, har kuma wata rana daga Talibans da ke Afghanistan.
Rahoton an shirya shi ta hanyar jami'in bincike na Mabiyu da kungiyar gano lafiya, wanda ke bin sawun gurbi na makotan ta duniya.
Rahoton ya kiyasta lambobin 'yan IS a Afghanistan sun kai 2,200, kuma duk da cewa shugabancinsu ya ragu, IS har yanzu ke da cikin shugabanninsa mutumin kasar Syria mai suna Abu Said Mohammad al-Khorasani.
Rahoton ya kuma ce, kungiyar kula da harkokin daukar hankali ta samu bayanai da cewa wani sakataren jihɔdin Islamic State, Abu Qutaibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraqi sun kawo kusan yau daga Turai zuwa Afghanistan.
Koda kuwa a tsawon yankin da suka bawa, (Kasar Islamiyya) har yanzu na iya yin harin da za su iya janyo hankali a wasu sassan ƙasar, ciki har da Kabul.
Yana da niyyar daukar wasu makiyaya daga Talibans wadanda suka yi mugun zahiri da wata yakin kulle, a cewar rahoton. Wannan yana nuni da kwangilar damuwan taliban da Amurka a watan Fabrairin baya.
Wannan yanke hukuncin yaki ya tattara damar yin amfani da Amurka ya kare nauyin shekaru 19 a Afghanistan, kuma ya bukaci Taliban su tabbatar da cewa ba za'a yi amfani da yankin su ba tare da yin yaki ba.
An yi tunanin cewa yanke hukuncin ma zai tabbatar da cimma nasarori na kowa-kowa na Taliban a kan yaki da IS.
Na biyu da kuma tabbacin matsayin mafi mahimmanci na cikakken janjawon ya kira ga hira tsakanin Taliban da jagorancin siyasa na Kabul.
Late Lahadi, Mashigar Harkokin tarayyar Amurka ta fitar da sanarwa ta ce mataimakin neman alheri na su Zalmay Khalilzad ya sake neman sabani a matsayin jihar neman fara harkokin, wadanda aka yi ta'aziyya sosai saboda cikin jam'iyyu na tattauna game da yancin daya bayan nan da sake shigo wa shugaban.
Sabilin da Amurka ta dauki nauyi ya bukaci gwamnatin Afghanin don a saki talabijin Taliban 5,000 da kuma Taliban na saki 1,000 daga gwamnati da sojojin kasar wanda ake kira shi a matsayin dangantakar kyauta  kafin hira.
Har yanzu gwamnatin ta ki yi wa kusa 600 'ya'yan Taliban da ta ce su ne masu ban-tsanani na ban mamaki da ta dauki mataki na daukar har su, da kuma bayyanawa kan yada su.
Taliban sun ki.
"Jam'iyyun sun kusa sosai da farawar hira tsakanin ‘yan Afghan, wani matakai mafi muhimmanci don kammala yakin Afaganistan na tsawon shekaru 40," inji bayanin hukumar yada labarai ta jihar Amurka.
"Ko da yake an samu ci gaban a kan canji na 'yan kisa, to amma damuwa ta tambaya don cika alaka guda."
Mai magana da yawun Siyasa na Taliban a wancan rana ya ce suna nan ɗaya don yin magana da shugabanin Siyasa na Kabul bayan halitta na Eid al-Adha a ƙarshe na wannan wata, idan an kai karshe a gurfanar da manyan ainihi.
