Makera ta huda: Banki na baya ta Birtaniya HSBC ya ki amincewa da "saitin kamasuwa" ga Kamfanin Huawei na Sin wajen binciken Amurka - RT Labarai Janairu
Bankin HSBC mai yada kudi a dukkan duniya da shugabanci a London ya dauki hanyar sadarwa ta hanyar shafukan sada zumunta domin fada, ba shi daidai da idanuwan jama'a daga cikin kasar Sin, cewa "ya yi yara" akan blue-chips na Huawei, wanda hakan ya kai ga kama wakilin masu cinikayya wajan kamfanin a Kanada.
A wani rubutu na WeChat da ba a samu shi ba, masaukin tallafi ya ce ba shi ne ke jawo bincike na Amurka a kan mafi girma mai samar da kayayyakin sadarwa a duniya, saboda bincike kan Huawei game da faruwa ya fara ne kafin kudin samun masaukin a wannan shekarar 2016.
"HSBC ba ta da wani kunci ga Huawei ba kuma ba ta yi 'kama' ga Huawei," bankin ya ce ranar Asabar, yana kuma ƙara da cewa ba za ta je ta wuce inda ta ke murkushe ko rufewa da kwatankwacin manyan al'umma.
Amsa zuwa buƙatun US DOJ [Iyakar Adalci na Amurka] kan samun bayanai, Ƙungiyar HSBC ta bayyana kawai haqa'iqin gaskiya.
HSBC ba ta "yi amfani da wani abu karya" ko "rufe" hujjoji ba.
Kuma a rt.com An cire Huawei daga shafin 5G a Ingila ya nuna cewa Amurka ke umarnin siyasa ta wurin ɓangaren Ingila - George Galloway ga Boom Bust
Rubutun da aka wallafa ya zama hana a kan dandamali tare da sanarwa cewa "yana kwace nau'in mulki" kuma ba'a samu shi yanzu ba.
Bayanin yana zuwa kawai bayan kama wajen magance Tafarkin asusun HbnC data saka asarar da WasanGidi abin fada akasarin hijiri marar dorawa da Zumunci na Kasuwar Huawei a cikin jarida da na jam'iyar yada labarai na da kudancin dabarun China.
Kamfanin ya kasance a tsakiyar jarabawar kudin jari na ƙasa da ƙasa cikin faduwar ma'aikaci da aka yi yarda da su a cikin shekarar da daya sama da ƙarshe tun daga lokacin da aka kama  CFO na Huawei, Meng Wanzhou a Disambar 2018 a Kanada bayan umarnin Amurka.
Meng ke fuskantar zaman kan gyara saboda zargin amfani da kamfanin kuma'la don kwace kayyada da suka ban Iran da kuma karya wa bankuna saki daga "aturmiyar" daidaituwa tsakanin Huawei da kamfanin Iran mai suna Skycom.
Bayan sabon shaida da aka ambata a Global Times, HSBC na da tabbacin cewa kamfanin kasar Sin ya sani game da al'adunsa da Skycom.
Bankin ya ce, ya yi niyyar "amfani" da gwamnatin Amurka domin tsammanin saɓo wanda ya fi wurin gano laifi a shekarar 2012, lokacin da bankin ya kasance na amincewa da kamfanin cin zamani da makiyaya kodai, har ma da jam'iyyun da suka shafi Iran.
An yi umarni a lokacin da za a biya kimanin $1.9 bilyan a matsayin kudade kuma don kauce wa wadannan yankin irin wannan.
"Bayanin da ya bayyana ya nuna cewa HSBC sun fahimci wannan dangantaka amma aka tsinka tunani yin amfani da takardun amini na asiri na abokan ciniki zuwa bangaren Amurka don hukumar gwamnatin Amurka zata yi watsi da laifin babban bankin Birtaniya da ba ta kama shi ta hanyar Sakamakon Hukunta da aka yi a 2012," inji jaridun a cikin daya daga cikin ma'aikatun da suka shafi batun.
A cikakken kai-tsaye, jaridar da gwamnatin Beijing ta kula da ita ta kara da cewa mai aikin tallafi, idan an tabbatar da cewa ya yi laifi na wannan "haɗin-gwiwa," zai iya fuskantar "sauran watsi" a kasar Sin, daya daga cikin kasashen babban kasuwa ga HSBC.
Ba tazarce ne farko da aka yi wa bankin mai suna kokarin kai harbi a makonni na baya.
Watan da ya gabata, HSBC ta rantsewa don taimakawa dokar tsaro ta kasa ta Hong Kong, birnin da kasuwancin ta fara dogo da wanda ya bayyana fiye da rabin ribar da ta ke samu.
Bankin ya fuskanci hujja daga bangaranci biyu - daga Yammacin, inda Kakakin Hukumar Kasa na Amurka Mike Pompeo yana kira goyon bayan "katon corporate," da Kudu, inda wadanda suka fito daga kasar Sin na yin kiran chat "daidaituwar goyon baya."
Makamai ta dama kan wutar motsi a kan kasar Lassen
