Aljeriya: Mutuwar Mahmoud Guemama - Aljeriya Ta Rasa Jagoran 'Yan Gudun Hijira, Babban Dodo, A cewar Shugaban Tebboune.
Algiers - Shugaban Ƙasa, Abdelmadjid Tebboune, ya aiko da sakon ta'aziyya ga 'yan majalisar ƙasa na (APN), Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, wanda ya rasu Juma'a, inda ya ce cewa Aljeriya "ta rasa ƙungiyar yan ƙasa mai rike hannu da babban ƙundin yarjejeniyar sa da ayyukan alƙalumai ɗin 'yan ƙasarsa da ƙasar."
Aljeriya ta rasa wani mai gwada lafiya, ta hanyar rasuwar Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, wani zama mai wakar da kishin kasa da shugabancin al'umma da kasa, mai da ba shi da wani hanu ba, mai da azancinsa kwato tsawon lokacin da ya dauki makami, tare da yan'uwan sa na Mujahideen, har zuwa lokacin da ya nemi kwanciya a ranar da muke faɗi ya zubar da shi in mun yarda da shi Allah," Shugaban ƙasa Tebboune ya rubuta a sakonsa na ta'zota da jinjina.
"Makwancin Mahmoud Guemama, sallamar gamon jininsa, ya kasance daga cikin takwarorin 'yan kishin kasa masu ta'aziyya da suka yi alwashin kallon kasarsu," inji Shugaban Jamhuriyar.
"Mutumin da ya rasu ya yi wa rayuwarsa gudunmawa don ceto Aljeriya daga wuyan makamantan bautar tazarce, ta hanyar shiga yankin Jihar jiniya a farkon rayuwa a 1960 a makarantar horo ta Tahart na wadda tarayya ta ɗaya."
"Makwancin shugaban kasa ya yi matukar san duniya da dulunsa na yaki da kuma murmushi a kan hanyar faruwa na kasar Algeria mai ci gaba da kuma sabuwa," in ji Shugaban Tebboune.
"A cikin kudancin ƙasar, mai zuƙata Marhum Mahmoud Guemama yana da yawa suna a matsayin mai gudanarwa, wanda ke shiga tsakanin 'yan'uwa a cikin ƙasar gabadaya kullum da wuta ta wa'azi ta kunna," inji Shugaban a sakon nasa.
"Dukkanin wannan al'ada da dabi'un ƙwayoyi ya bamu da sha'awar juna na marigayi Mahmoud Guemama bisa juna da amincin mutanen Tamanrasset wanda suka zabi shi don wakiltar musu a Majalisar Tarayyar Mutane (APN) kusan shekaru da dama, inda ya kasance shugaban kuma kiran makiyaya akan damuwa na yankin da kuma damuwar jama'a, har ma mai waka da ƙafe-kafewar duk Algeriyawa," in ji Shugaban Tarayya.
"Dukkanin magance ta'azi ba zai yi tasiri wajen gabatar da goyon bayan ga mujahedin Mahmoud Guemama, alheri ya zo masa."
"Ya kasance yana barinmu yau a lokacin da Aljeriya na bukatarsa," inji Shugaban.
Ina rokon Ubangijin ban mamaki ya bawa mutumin rasuwa shugabancin jikinsa na Maras Kuskure, ya karɓi shi cikin ƙasar Aljanna mai yawa tare da shuhada'i da masu adalci.
Ina kuma addu'a ga Ubangiji ya ba'yi wa iyalinsa da masu taimakonsa hakuri da kwanciyar hankali...babu ikon ko iko a wurin Allah ne," Shugaban Tarayya ya karshe.
Taron Seattle: Wutar da Murar Kwakwalwa a Matsayin Dubu Masu Yawo Ta Cikin Birni
SAETAL - Bayan makonni da adawa tsakanin masu shigar da ninkaya a Portland, Oregon, 'yan kungi tare da kimanin mutane 2,000 sun tara a Saetal a ranar Asabar, suka yi karko mijin hanyoyi suna fadarsu da 'yan sanda.
Uku na'urar 'yan sanda sun samu rauni, wanda ya hada da wanda ake kula da shi a asibiti saboda rauni mai wuya da ya samu daga layin hatsin baki, da kuma kowane 16 na masu shiga hukumar tsaro sun yi wa'adinjiyar da zarar yamma, 'yan sanda sun ce.
Yin sanya haruffai iri kamar "Feds Go Home" da kuma yin mandongan 'yan kallo, masu hira suka tsaya a wurin kowane gidan kararin yara da ake ginawa don suka yiwa bangarorin iska dutse.
Wasu sun gwastar damfaraɗi na cikin kantunan kusa na shagunan kasuwanci.
'Yan sanda sun fuskanci taron mutane a unguwar Capitol Hill, suka yi amfani da makaman bayanai da shayen suya kafin su fara kama mutane cikin kulle.
Bipasha Mukherjee, 52, daga Kirkland, Wash., ta ce tana makiyaya kan titi tun Mayu, inda ta ce wasu taktikai masu baki da 'yan sanda ke yi mata damuwa.
"Babu wannan ƙasar da na shiga," inji Hajiya Mukherjee, wacce ta iso daga ƙasar India da baya sama da shekaru 30.
Yana kamata muna yi ƙarfi na haifar da ƙasa mai faɗaɗi ne kuma ƙasa mai ɗanɗano na 'yan sanda.
Michaud Savage na Seattle ya ce, tuntubarmu an yi su ne wajen hukumomin yankin da kuma rufe su na ma'aikatan gwamnatin tarayya da suka yi nasarar jitse da tuntubar ta Portland wanda ya dade.
Malam Savage ya ce hanyoyin tsaro a Portland, wadanda suka hada da amfani da gas na kuka da makamancin hukumomin gaggawa, sun kasance kunnasawa da ba daidai ba.
"Ya zama teku mai yawa a hanya mai zurfi sosai," Mista Savage yace yayin da yake wanke idanunsa daga rogo mai safin yaki da kuma hada rauni a hannunsa daga fres na sofatarum.
Rasūwars George Floyd a hannun 'yan sanda a Minneapolis a watan May ya jiyasta makiyayya masu yawa da suka tarwatse miliyoyin mutane zuwa titunannin a birnin dasu, amma wakilan hakan sun rage a yayin da yawa a cikin birnensu.
Seattle da Portland, kuma dai, sun ga sharaɗin da aka sabunta zuwa.
Mabiyanta Seattle a wani lokaci sun dauki alaka da doguwar rumbu na unguwar Capitol Hill kuma suka bayyana yankin kamar yankin da ya tsayawa kansa.
Bayan wani jerin kicikon da suka jawo hankalin 'yan sanda su dakile yankin, rashin shimfida ya ragu.
Portland, a duk da haka, ya ci gaba da shuwagar, tare da wasu daga cikin shuwagin gwamnatin tarayya mai nauyi a birnin.
Bayan Shugaban Trump ya fitar da umarnin shuwagabanni don kare hotuna da mulki na gwamnati, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Ƙasa ta yaki da ƙungiyoyin furuci a birnin, a farfajiyar barkatai da ke haifarwa da manyan masu yawaitar talaka, ayyukansa na mai ba da shawara da kiran shugabannin yankuna da ƙungiyoyi da su bar.
Muhawarin yara a cikin birnin sun kai dubu dayawa, kuma nuna musu yana ci gaba a nan.
Wannan makon, 'yan sanda na gwamnati suka tura wani kwamando masu hikima zuwa Seattle, kuma masu shigar da amsoshin basu damuwar zuwan wannan taimakon kasuwa ne damuwa da ya jawo yau na Asabar.
Yayin da motsin Portland ya tsaya a cikin birnin, zanga-zangar Asabar ta yanke hanyoyi na gabas daga cikin birni mai tsarki, inda kotun koli na hukumar gwamnatin tarayya ke ciki.
Virginia Beach ya kaurace tawagar kabilu na kungiyar Confederate
VIRGINIA BEACH, Va. -- Birnin Virginia Beach ya cire dokar karamar hukumar Confederates daga filin jirgi na jama'a a ranar Asabar, a kasa da kwana biyu bayan majalisar kotu ta birnin ta yi zaben kawai don yin hakan.
