Matakan ƙaryar ƙungiyar ta'addanci a ƙarƙashin mulki na Labour sun nemi a janye Corbyn ko su hadu da shari'ar muƙabalanci
Aikin hakane zai iya biyan kudaden kashi tsakanin Naira ₦3miliyan zuwa ₦8miliyan, a cikin rahotanni.
Yanzu shugaban Keir Starmer ke karkashin matsala domin tattaro gwamnan Mr Corbyn.
Daren jiya ma'aikatan tare da suka yi aiki sun ce zasu koma hannun hukuma idan aka kore Mr Corbyn daga jam'iyyar.
Jam'iyyar Aiki ta saukake yin sharhi akan matsayar da aka bukata.
Duk da haka, 'Yan majalisar tarayya ta Jam'iyyar All Progressives Congress Jon Trickett yace: "Akwai bukatar da ake yi a cikin haka ba daidai bane."
Masu taya wa Mista Corbyn sun ce Mista Starmer yana bukatar bunkasa kalubalantar 'yan Takara ta siyasar Tory a kan kula da annobar coronavirus maimakon yin sako har zuwa cikin rikicin da ya shafi Jam'iyyar Labarai.
Wani abokan tazarce na Jam'iyyar Aiki ta hanyar bayani ga Daily Mail cewa za su dauki mataki na kotu ko da Meeya Starmer ya kore Meeya Corbyn.
"Mena, yana da gaske, ya sa jam'iyyar Aiki ta kasance konkurenci mai amfani."
