'Yan Sanda ke yi amfani da kayayyaki masu raunin daƙiƙa, yayin da tarayyar dandali ta ci gaba
Yayin da damuwa ta ci gaba tsakanin 'yan sanda da ma'aikatantu a Portland da sauran kasa, hira ke tafiya game da yadda 'yan sanda zasu iya rage amfani da karfi mai mutum kash.
Wasu kamfanoni sun kara matakin bayarwa don samar da kayayyakin sadarwa masu zamani kamar makamai daga nesa don 'yan sanda su amfani da su makuɓaɓɓiyar kayan aikinsu kamar gas da gugu, kwalbaran kwallon gumi da kwayoyin wuta.
Kungiyar yanayin jama'a na 'yan kasashen waje (Amnesty International) ta bincika hotuna daga bidiyo 500 daga shugabannin da suka faru ne tsakanin Mayu 26 zuwa Junairu 5 kuma ta sami dambuwa 125 cikin azarce a cikin jihohi 40 da Karamar Hukuma na Columbia.
"Mun ga amfani mai iliminmi na kayyade gas na wasa, kayyade ruwan biber, kwayoyin biber, 40 millimeter na gudunmawarka, kusan kowane hadin gwiwar makami mai qoshin kara a yau da kullum ana amfani da su a matsayin wadanda basu dace ba," inji Ma'aikatar Bincike na Makaman Amnesty International, Brian Castner.
Ko da yake, wasu suna nanatawa cewa samuwa da zaɓuɓɓuka ya bayar da muhimmanci domin kwato bukatar makami.
"Duk wadannan kayayyaki ya kamata su kasance hannu da 'yan sanda su amfani da su, ba tare da amfani da karfi mai mummunar halaka da bindiga ba, saboda ita ce kawai sana'ar a Amurka inda jama'a suke ba ka damuwa a kan rayuwarka," in ji Corey Pegues, wanda ya kasance na farko a matsayin Janar na 'Yan Sandan New York.
