200 da yawa ma'aikatan kula da wuta na amsa ga Wutar Karen mai wulla a Jurupa Valley - CBS Los Angeles
JURUPA VALLEY (CBSLA) - Wata wutar makamai ta fito ranar Asabar da safe a cikin Jurupa Valley, inda akayi amfani da ma'adinin wuta sama da 200 don magance ta.
Wutar makamai Karen ta anko ne kusan minti hudu bayan Azahar 3, a kan titin Sierra Avenue da Karen Lane.
Wutar da kogi ta kara daga kashi 5 zuwa 10 ekras zuwa kashi 250 a matsayin 8 na dare.
Yauk'in gudana da aka goge k'arshe ya kasance a 50% da kuma k'aramun makiyaya 225 daga Cal Fire, Riverside County Fire Department, City of Corona Fire Department, da San Bernardino County Fire suna kan titin yaki da wutan.
Ci gaban wutar da ta yi tsaki an tsare, amma ana sa ran an jira su kwana daf da daf domin kalli yanayi.
Babu raunuka ko kuma kawo gudunmawar gida da aka tattara ba, da kuma babu umarnin da aka bukaci mutane su fita daga gida ba.
Sierra Avenue tsakanin Armstrong da Kwararren San Bernardino ya rufe.
Babban shugaban UN ya kasa zuwa Pakistan, yana bayyana matsalar tashar jirgin kasa
ISLAMABAD (AP) - Shugaban majalisar dinkin duniya ta United Nations, ya sanar ranar Lahadi cewa ya kawo gaba wata ziyara da ya tsara zuwa Pakistan "saboda wasu matsaloli na gudanarwa na tashar jiragen sama."
Safiinacin Turkiyya Volkan Bozkir ya zaba shugaban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya na 75 ga watan da ya gabata a watan da ya gabata, kuma an saba masa zuwa Islamabad ranar Lahadi.
Amma cikin rubutu na Twitter, ya ce ziyarar babban birnin Pakistan dole ta jira.
Wazirin harkokin wajen Pakistan, Shah Mahmood Qureshi ya yi tweeting amsa Bozkir cewa "ina jiran maka maraba a Pakistan da zarar kazo maki ziyara mai dorewa da kuma mai amfani."
Ranar da ya gabata, Qureshi mai murna, yayin da yake sanar da zuwansa, ya yi alkawari zai yi magana akan yawan matsalolin da suka hada da Bozkir, wadannan ke kunshi Kashmir, inda wadancan take tsakanin Pakistan da kasar gidan guguwar India kuma na biyu kowa na ci gaba da shi.
Pakistan da Indiya sun yi waɗannan biyu daga cikin tashoshin uku na yaki akan yankin da ke kan lambun jirgin saman da suka samu cigaba daga mulkin Birtaniya a shekarar 1947.
Biyan kashi biyu na yawan kwace-kwace a Kashmir, wanda ya ke jawo raunuka ga sojoji da rayuwa marayu a kan biyan kashi.
Pakistan ke so Mabiyu Na'urar kawai su yi gaba wajen rundunar masalatar Kashmir a karkashin wadatasu bisa bayarwa mutanen da ke zaune a yankin Himalayan dama su tsaya ma'anar shiga kasar India, tare da Pakistan ko kuma su zabe kasuwa.
