Bindigar UFC Correia ya samu bugawa bayan ya juya baya ga ɗan wasa sakamakon jin sigar ya kare (BIDIYO) - RT Labarai na Wasanni
Brazillian bantamweight Bethe Correia mai tsaro a UFC amma ya yi kuskure na amata kamar yadda ya danne kansa akan Pannie Kianzad, kuma ya tunani rahupawa ya kare a wasan da suka fafata a Fight Island, kuma shi ya samu matsala a saboda haka.
Kamar yadda daya kare na farko na buga wakarsu a karkashin jerin fina-finan a Abu Dhabi, Correia mai shekaru 37 ya yi kuskure yana dauka daukakar 'yan jimilla na 10 na lokaci don karshe na hazawa ne, ya zaro kafadarsa kafin ya juya baya ga Kianzad, sannan koma cikin tangararsa.
Dan wasan kungiyar Suwidi ya yi amfani da damuwa ba tare da motsin rai ba, ya kama magajiyar sa hannun dama sannan ya kara da gogewar bugawa domin rufe Correia akan kofin kwaski.
Saurin bayyana a cikin matsala, nan da nan mutumin Birazil ya sake amfani da sarari domin kwantar da hargitsi kuma ya kuma warkewa Kianzad baya kafin an kira karshe na dare na gaskiya.
"Me ya faru a can? Kai ban sha'awa," wasu daga cikin maƙaloli na ESPN+ suka ji ana faɗaɗawa.
Ya kasance kawai ɗaya daga cikin dare mai damuwa ga sabon mai shawo kan kwallo na bantamweight Correia, wanda ya fadi a kasa ga dukiyar karɓar da ya samu fiye da ta daya, shi ne rabin rasa ɗin a cikin taci guda uku da ya yi a kan octagon. Hakan ya bar ma'ana ɗin ta na tanadi na kwallo a 11-5, tare da raba ɗaya.
Ga Kianzad mai haifar da Iran, 28, shi ne ci gaba na biyu sau daga janye gaba bayan nasarar ta kwana da Jessica-Rose Clark a UFC Fight Night a Moscow zuwa baya a Nuwamba.
Kianzad yanzu an samu 13-5 a duk fadin duniya kuma 2-1 a cikin UFC, da matar da aka sani da 'Banzai' take neman mayar da halitta a jerin 135lbs.
Wani bangare a dare, mai bokon kasar Australia, Robert Whittaker ya ci gawa mai bai wa kasar Ingila Darren Till a zanga-zangar nau'ikan arewa, yayin da mai baro'ar dambe kasar Rasha, Khamzat Chimaev ya yi tarihin da ba zai manta ba ne a cikin 10 kwanakin a Fight Island, muddin tsakanin nasarori a cikin zamani na yanzu na UFC.
Watford ya fice daga gasar Premier League saboda Aubameyang ya jefa Arsenal cikin nasara
Wasu daga cikin 'yan wasan Watford sun kasa kan gudunmawarsu; wadanda suka wuce wajen funnel ba tare da kokarin daɗi ba.
Fararen kwantini ya ƙona dab da kukanku a cikin shekaru biyar da suka gudana a Premier League, kuma babu wani mai cewa, lokacin da bai waɗanda ya buƙatar su jefa samɓadar tuwon gida zuwa Arsenal, sun kasa ƙaryar da wani jagora.
Wannan shine kyautar da ta cike da laushi, adawa da kuma gwagwarmaya wanda ke bayyana a cikin ayyukansu na fiye da mako biyar da suka gabata, amma ya zo daidai bayan da aka gama, kamar yadda 'yan adawa suka kusa mayar da rukuniyar da suka kasa kwana a karo na yau.
Idan Emiliano Martínez bai yi nasara a hankali a dakata kafa na Danny Welbeck 16 mintuna kafin lokacin ba, da zarar abokin kakansa ya buga shi ya shiga Watford dai-dukan biyu da ke cikin tsaro ba, to akwai yiwuwar suka iya gama komai da komai na ƙarni.
A ƙarshe suka kasa, kuma mai kula da su, Hayden Mullins, zai yi tunanin cewa bai wani lokaci ba ya samu wannan aikin da ba shi da kyau ba idan ƙungiyarsa ta nuna yiwuwar ƙoƙari da ta yi kafin.
Cikin jimawa ba su yi kyau ba, amma kuma ba haka shi ne kungiyar da ta aiki da su ba.
Daya daga cikin kampeɲin miskinawa ba zai iya wulakanta mulki ba, amma kuwa ba haka heƙar da ɗan'adamawa Pozzo da suka dora ba su nuna damuwa cewa za su yi mawuyacin yi daga ƙarshen biyu.
Yana da wahatsa zaɓen mutane da alaka da cewa Watford na sauya yanadaula ya ragu da hanyar gudanar da hukuma.
Masu zaman kansu na gaba na dae-dae - ko a ma'anar mawuyacin hali - zai kasance na 12 a cikin shekara takwas da kuma akwai yawan hawa iska na sabulu mai sabulu zai iya shafawa cikin.
Troy Deeney yana fuskantar raguwa koda kuwa ya shiga jerin shiga matakan riqo a filin wasan Emirates.
Masu wasa za su tafi, Ismaïla Sarr yana nuni nan cewa ba ya yi kama ya ke buga wasan gasar Championship a Satumba ba, kuma hannun mai kwanciya ya kamata ya zama muhimmi.
Babu wani abu mai tsantsi a kan sabis na tashin hankalin jama'a wanda Mikel Arteta ya kira "wasanni na basketball" watakila, kuma babu shakka ya kasance abin sha'awa mai kyau.
Arteta ya ce bayanin da Watford ke ƙara "watau ne," kuma ya tabbatar da haka a matsayin kalaman ƙwallon ɗan wasa wato "shawara, tsaya a gaban."
Ba shakka har yanzu suke bukata: duk wata shawarar wani tsari da zai iya yiwuwa yakamata ya koma labari ne don tabbatar da cewa ba za su ji dadin yadda abubuwan suka shafe ba idan basu hada hannu da makomar ba.
Sai dai suka yarda da kittan kwanji kalilan da wuri.
