oOh! Media ya tattara kuɗin kasafai a watan da ya gabata domin samar da sigogin kudi lokacin da annobar ta fara damu masu tallafawa.
Mambobi sun ce cewa kamfanonin ke magana akan yadda za su iya mayar da kasa sabo na girman ragewa ta wannan hari ta hanyar rage ciniki don wuraren da suka saba ko ta biyar makiyancin kudin samarwa, wadda aka saba samun ta farko lokaci da aka sanya amincewa.
Daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin kwamfuta ya nuna cewa, an yi alkawari kan samuwa da kashi 85 per cent daga jajircewar kudadensu a matsayin kiraye.
Wasu kagaggun labarai suna da shafukan da ke ba su damuwa na rage alkawarin kadan idan yawan mutane a wani yanki ya ragu da wani sashi, amma ba a gane ko wannan shari'a a cikin kowane daga cikin kagaggun labarai na yanzu tsakanin kamfanonin ban daɗa da ma'aikatansu.
A lokacin daya, kamfanonin suna ba da ƙididdige masu girma ga masu tallafawa don ɗaukar wurare ɗin a kan banbancuka horo da kuma bada su damar yi ƙyauta ta kyauta wajen samar da kuɗin da suke bayarwa.
Alamun labarai a cikin Kauyen Babban Birnin Sydney da karkashin jihohi da cewa ta zama tare da wasu girmamawa bakwai suke kokarin cika duk wadannan dawrakun da take yiwuwa.
Amma wasu wurare - kamar oOh! media na 40 x 10 mita babban alamun a filin jirgin sama na Sydney - an gyara su.
oOh! Media ya ki yayi magana, amma a wani taron Macquarie Australia a watan Mayu, ya nuna cewa za a iya samun fiye da miliyan dubu 20 a matsayin kudin karɓin kiran gida.
JC Decaux ya ki yi magana ba.
Filaye da kayan gudanarwa na jama'a suna samuwar kwamfuta ayyuka ga kamfanoni masu rufe murtani.
Bayanin Kungiyar Tallafawa na Waje ta shekarar 2019, kudin tallafawa - dangane da jirgin saman - ya kai miliyan $169.4, yayin da kudin daga saman dokokin gida da wajen basu da motoci a kan hanya ya kai miliyan $266.5.
Kasuwancin JC Decaux na da albashinsu da Makewayar Huda na Sydney, Yarra Trams, Perth Airport da Buses na Sydney. oOh! Media na da bayanan hoto a wurare iri daban-daban kamar bangaren kangarori na Qantas, waje hudar Sydney, Adelaide Airport, Darwin Airport da cikin tsakar daki a makewayan gida a Sydney da Melbourne.
Karafun masu shiƙarɗi na Jirgin sama na Melbourne da Kereke maƙera na Sydney suna ci gaba a cikin Pandemic, kuma babu wani ra'ayi na rasɗɨn ɗauke.
Melbourne shine yanar gizo mafi girma na biyu a Australia da kafin koronavirus ya kasance da hawa miliyoyi a kowane shekara.
A sakon kudaden da aka samu a Fabrairin, oOh! Media ya ce ya samu $65.9 miliyan daga ƙungiyar 'fly' nasa, wadda take ƙasar kudi mai yawan Dala daga jirgin saman Hukumar Shiryawa ta Sydney.
Kudin 'commute', wanda ya kunshi ayyuka na jirgin kasa da abubuwan gida na titi wanda Adshel yake mallaki kafin ya siyo oOh!, ya zama $234.8 miliyan.
JC Decaux Australia ya samu kudin shiga Naira 37.7 miliyan daga sauka a shekarar 2018, bisa wani rahoto da aka fitar kan nutsuwar tattalin arziki a shekarar 2018 da aka ajiye ga kamfanin Kudaden Rufe Ko Gwaji Wajen Australia.
