Yan sandan Kenya sun kama bayan kisan mutum mai fatal dake faruwa a Garissa
Biyan hukumar tsaro biyu a Kenya sun yi matakin kama sakamakon harin da aka yi inda mutane biyu suka mutu.
Yakin kama ya faru a kasuwar Soko Ng'ombe a gabashin garin Garissa a ranar Asabar, lokacin da mutane ke shiga yaki kan kama wani mutum da aka yi zargin kashe mai.
Makamai biyu suna masu ana zuwa an ce suna Aden Abdi Madobe da Muhiyadin Adow Shibin.
Makon dogaro na 'yan sanda na Kenya ya fara bincike kan harin da aka yi.
Zai hada da "bincike na hukunci" na bindigogi na 'yan sanda.
Majalisar Tarayyar Garissa Aden Duale ya kira mutuwar "mummuna" kuma ya shaida kan "haƙƙin ƴan sanda" a wani baya'ɗi da ya saka a Facebook.
Mawallafa sun bayyana damuwa game da hukumar tsaro lokacin annobar cutar.
Bayanai daga kungiyar 'yansandan duniya, 'yan sanda na Kenya sun kashe mutane 21 tun daga Watan Maris saboda rashin bi dangane da nawar cutar korona kamar kuma karbar makamanci da rufe fuska.
A farkon wannan wata, 'yan sanda a babban birnin Nairobi sun yi harbe shara da kuma kama wasu masu shiga cikin horo na Saba Saba na kowane shekara - wani horo da ya fara zuwa shekaru 30 da suka gabata a kan zaman kulle na shugaban kasa na lokacin, Daniel arap Moi.
Mawallafa sun ce wannan shekarar da aka yi wa taron na yi mako na cikin ita ta samu karin sanyi ne ta anger saboda shagunan yan sanda da suka yi a lokacin hana motsi a dukkanin lokaci da Covid-19.
Shivraj Singh Chouhan kan gwajin cutar Covid mai Sauri
Gwamnan Jihar Madhya Pradesh, Shivraj Singh Chouhan, wanda ya tabbatar da cewa ya samu damun COVID-19 ranar Asabar, ya yi tweeting ranar Lahadi safe don fada cewa "ya kamata" kuma ya bayar wa ma'aikatan fagen dangantakar makonni bayanai a kokarin ganin an kasheta cutar coronavirus.
Ministan Sufuri ya sake dakatar da sakonshi na jiya, inda yake nemi mutane su bi shawarwari, irin su saduwa da al'umma da amfani da hanyoyin fuskantar fuska.
Yi haƙuri, abokaina. Baɗaɗar koronavirus ɗanƙon mallakar juna, da suke haɗuwa da ra'ayin kansu ba tare da jin daɗin kuma, ya yi amfani. Na yi wa dukkan ɗanƙon koronavirus na jahar taɓa, yace Masu dem Chouhari tare da makale a cikin Asibitin Chirayu na Bhopal, inda aka dauroshi jiya.
"Tsaya dakin biyu, washe hannuwanku a lokuta dayawa, kuma sai masu koyar da fuska - wadannan ne babban kayan da muke dashi dan kewaye cutar coronavirus. Ina kira ga dukan mutane - amfani da wadannan kayayyaki maki da wurin mahaliccinku," yace.
"Dukkanku ku kula da kanku, ku zama lafiya da tsaro. Wannan shine abin da nake roko ga Allah," ya kara da cewa Mr Chouhan.
A ranar Satumba, Mallam Chouhan ya yi tweeting cewa ya sami damuwar cutar ba da jimawa ba wato, kwararrun hanyoyin da ya bi wajen kawo ƴan tozalin da kuma ya yi ƙirƙira cewa "kwararrun darajar ya yi tarɓawa cutar makaryata."
Yauwa game da sako a wurin Mr. Chouhan ya ce, koda yake da damuwa ta cutar, babu bukatar tsorata" kuma ya yi kira ga masu bayanai su nemo kula da kansu.
"Idan ka kamu, babu damuwa. Kada ka boye alamun da suka shafa ka, sai dai ka sanar da likitoci nan take, don haka za a fara magani. Maganin da ya yi waqtu zai sa ka lafiya," ya ce.
Madhya Pradesh yana da kusan dubu 27,000 na cututtukan COVID-19, daga cikinsu fiye da dubu 7,600 suna aiki kuma raba ₈₉₉ da mutuwa mai alaƙa da kwayar cuta.
Indiya ta tuna da yawa a cikin matsalar cutar COVID-19 a mako na baya, da fiye da dabaru 45,000 na sabo an gano kowane ranar tun ranar 23 ga watan Juli.
Yawan lafiyar da aka tabbatar da cewa an samu daga koronavirus ke kusan kai mafi yawan 14 lakh; daga wannan, fiye da 4.67 lakh suna da matukar lafiya da kuma fiye da 32,000 sun mutu saboda cutar.
Tsadar faduwar matakan cutar, wanda ya yi jitu hamyarawa da kuma gabatar da katiyoyin wargazanci a wuraren da basa da wadansu a kasar, ya kawo farin jini ga Indiya ta hudu a cikin jerin kasashen da cutar ta haddasa mafi yawan.
Kawai Amurka (41.78 lakh matakan) da Birazil (23.94 lakh matakan) su ne mafi tushen wahala.
Ministan ciki na Tunisia ya zama sabon shugaban gwamnati, zai kafa gwamnati a cikin wata daya
Ministan Ciki na Tunis Hichem Mechichi ya yi nisa ya halarta shugaban kasa, ofishin shugaban kasa ya ce, a tsakanin tsuntsaye na siyasa a cikin jam'iyyun masu zaman kansu a kasar Arewa ta Afirka.
Mai shekara 46, mai yada shar'ia ya gaza Elyes Fakhfakh, wanda ya rage matsayin shugaban gwamnati a wannan watan.
Amma Mechichi bai kasance daya daga cikin sunayen da jam'iyyan siyasar mulkin suka shaida wa Shugaban Kasa Kais Saied ba.
Bayanin da ya biyo bayan sanarwar Asabar, Mechichi ya ce zai "aiki don kafa gwamnati da zata sanya kowane mai bukata tun daga jama'a da addini".
Tunisiya ta samu yabo sosai a matsayin labarai na musamman na koma demokradiyya bayan yaki na Arab dake kutsawa daga taron domin koyon kanji a shekarar 2011.
Ammata kuma shugabanninsa suna kokarin bi damuwar jama'a na Tunisiya kuma tattalin arziki na nesa na nesa da karamin lafiya ya sha taurin kai saboda rufe iyakokin kasar ne na saboda annobar COVID-19.
Cutar ta kashe kusa da mutane 50 da kuma suka kamu da fiye da dubu 1,400 a Tunisiya.
Kamar yadda ya kasance dan majalisar gaban gwamnan cikin gwamnatin da ta gabata, Mechichi shi ma wakilin shugaban kasa Saied ne, ya kula da al'amuran kotu.
Ya yi tafiyar ne kuma shugaban ma'aikatar shugabanci a Wizarar Tsaro da kuma ya aiki a Wizarar Al'amuran Jama'a.
Yanzu-yanzu ya samu wata daya don kafa gwamnati, wanda zai ga shawara mai kud'i a majalisar dattawan kuma zai bukaci bobbin yadda ya shiga don samu nasara.
Idan ba haka ba, majalisar zartarwa za a koma ta kassara kuma za a gudanar da sabuwar zaben farko a cikin watanni uku.
A zaben da ya gabata na Oktoba, jam'iyyar Ennahdha ta samu jagora amma ta kasa ta sami wata yar kasa da yawa kuma ta amince ta shigar da gwamnatin tarayya.
Fakhfakh na ƙari a ranar 15 ga watan Yuli, bayan fiye da kwanaki biyar a mulki, wanda ya haddasa shakka mai dauke da amfani a cikin al'umma a wancan lokaci daya kamata sumame makiyayin tattalin arziki dokin cutar damuwa.
Rage tsayawa ya ƙara daukar nauyin siyasa tare da Ennahdha kan zargin Fakhfakh da yawaita ɗauki shuni.
Ƙarin kai tsakanin shugaban da ya yi shekara 47 da Ennahdha ya yi nisa tun daga zaben na watan Oktoba.
Fakhfakh ya yi kasa a ranar da jam'iyyar ta sanya shawara mai ban tabbanci a kan sa.
Ennahdha ta kafa zunubin wani mabagacin dan siyasa domin shugaban gwamnatin, amma ya kasa samun goyon bayan majalisar dokokin kasar, wanda ya sa shugaban kasar ya nada wani sabon shugaban wizarin siyasar kudi Fakhfakh domin wannan aiki.
Da fuskantar yin zaben sabuwar, Ennahdha ta amince karshe ta shiga kayar baya tare da gwamnatin tarayya.
Motar ta wuce cikin tarukan mutane, mai shago ya yi butulci a Colorado
AURORA, Colo. (AP) - Wata mota ta wuce cikin taro da kuma wani mai shaida ya yi barazana a kananan birnin Denver na Aurora a cikin nuni kan zulumin fata.
Fadar 'Yan Sanda ta Aurora ta bayyana a Twitter cewa masu neman zaman lafiya suna tafiya akan Hanyar 225 na Jirgin Saman karshen Asabar lokacin da mota ta wuce cikin.
'Yan sanda sun ce mai shiga ya sake wani makami, ya kai wani mutum daya kamarsa wanda ya kaiwo asibiti a matsayi mai nagarta.
Hukumomi sun ce motar ta janyo wani abu kuma suna bincike.
Makiyaya kuma suka katse tagulla daga makonniyar hukuma da wuta aka fara a cikin ofishin, 'yan sanda suka bayyana.
An yankewa taron bambanci sananne kuma 'yan sanda suka umarci masu shiga horar da yankin, hukumar ta bayyana.
Tayar da al'amarin ya zama madaidaici a bakin hulda na kwanaki a saboda shakkuwa kan matsalar yanadunia bincike da suka yi a Portland, Oregon daidai lokacin da manyan kamfanoni suka aiko wa su tallafin hujja.
'Yan sanda sun bayyana zanga-zanga a Seattle a ranar Asabar.
Murtata sun fito ne bayan rasuwar George Floyd, wanda ya mutu a Minnesota a kan 25 ga May, bayan wani ɗan sanda ɓature ya rufe shi da wuyansa. Hakan ya kawo haduwa da wasu ninkaya daga hannu na jan toro da suka baransu.
A Colorado, masu shiga wa'azi suna nuna damuwa akan mutuwar Elijah McClain, wanda aka tsayar da shi ta hanyar yanar gizo a Aurora a Satumba 2019 bayan da mai kirar 911 ya rika shi da mamaki.
'Yan sanda suka yi masa kama da hannu a cikin bakin fari, sannan likitan gudanarwa suka ba da 500 milligrams na ketamin, wani maganin sha, don sa shi tsayar da hankali.
Ya shiga kashin zuciya, bayan haka aka bayyana cewa bai da tunani a kansa ba yace kuma aka kaishi daga taimakon rayuwa.
Babban tabbacin tekuwar Lake Tahoe an cinye ta da canjin yanayi
Kudu Ta Taho, Kwalifoniya - Babu wanda ya hana, har ma a watan jibi, mutane suna cikin tarin mutane a Pantami ta Taho.
"Ina so kusa da kauyen da aka yi camp, shirye-shiryen kayan gudu da tafiya a cikin teku a jikin tadawo," ce mace mai suna Dakota.
"Wannan abu ne mai kyau da kowane mutum yana so ya ziyarci," in ji Emerica Benitas.
Wacece dalilin da ke sa kasuwancin kama tasowa na Matt Meunier yana ci gaba da kasancewa mai daraja, har ma cikin annobar cutar.
Ya ce yana ganin "ingancin bayyanawa. Lake Tahoe shi ne jirgin ruwa mai tsaro, mafi kyawun, na yinku, ina ganin, a kasar."
Yanzu labarin mugu: Tadon Lake Tahoe bai kasance daidai ba, ba kuma tsantsar ba, kamar yadda ya kasance da shi tun daga shekara biyu da dubu da suka wuce.
"Abinda muke gani mafi girma da yawa shi ne a kan dutse," inji Meunier.
"Kana samun wannan kwanar baki mai ban tsoro akan dutse."
Sauyi na yanayi, masana suna ganin, ya shafi tsinkayar ruwa da hakan nan, kwarin gwiwa.
Kuma mutane miliyan 15 suna ziyarci teku kowace shekara - tare da sharan gawarwakin da suka barawa.
Meunier ya ce tafiye-tafiye na nesa don wanke kasa na tabkin gaba ya sami shara mara hanzari.
"Sannan idan na ce makamai ƙauna, na nufi '60s, '70s," in ji Meunier.
"Gidajen giya, gidajen sobar soda, makamancin kwalbalan canji daga zamanin da suka wuce."
Masana sukan kula da ingancin Te-shan Tahoe a kowace shekara ta hanyar saukar da wani wando fari, sannan su kwatanta yadda za su iya ganinsa har zuwa mak'abarta.
Profesa Geoff Schladow na UC Davis ya ce wannan shine "alamar muhimmanci na ya wani teku ke cikin lafiya."
Yau da aka yi kwantirawar shekara da ta gabata, tsananin ingancin teku ya kai kusan 80 kafu.
Hakanan ka iya ganin cakar kwalba 80 feet a kasa.
Amma, ka duba wannan, kimanin shekaru 20 da suka wuce, ingancin teku ya kasance futi 100.
Wancan ne salon tattalin arziki da masana suna kokarin sake jefar.
Amma suna yaki da hanyoyin da sauyin yanayi ya shafa, a Yi wa tafkin wani inganci da kuma wani abu da aka kara wa tafkin a cikin shekarar 1960: Wani karamin kankana mai bazuwa da aka kawo domin ciyar da kasa.
Ba ya yi aiki ba.
"Da zarar yayyankun dobari suka shigo, babu wani mai wanzar da ingancin dabino a cikin tabki," inji Schladow.
Matsalolin da suka dace suna fuskantar teku da kogin ruwa na duniya baki ɗaya.
"Darin ilimin nan shi ne, idan ba za ku iya yin shi a Tahoe ba, to mey kuma damuwa ce da ke akwai ga dukkanin kogin da estuaries, cinyoyin da tadaborin a ƙasar da ba za su sami matakain irin, tsarin kayan aikin da suke da shi?" inji Schladow.
Meunier ya ce yana da "tumaki" saboda "idan akwai kyautar makanta na pandemi, na yi alkawarin cewa duniya ta dawo kan gafara kanta idan mu sai muguwa, muguwar dan adam, daga kan ta kuma zamana ta samu. Akwai hujjoji a can yanzu."
Mijin da Matarsa SUNA TASHE a filin kare na California saboda ba su yi amfani da lambu a fusace ba yayin da suke ci abinci (BIDIYO) - RT USA News
Akwai kallon ban da fuskantar kai, sannan akwai haragin kai zalla babba.
Wata makiya da miji daga California da ke cin abincin rana tare da kyan gudbawa a fagen kare sun sha wahala na biyu, lokacin da mace makiya ce ta kwalata su don sun fushi da ita game da yin amfani da masken amma... yayin da suke ci.
Ash O'Brien da mijinta Jarett Kelley sun ce suna daukar abinci a filin kare na Dusty Rhodes a San Diego a ranar Alhamis, tare da suka kai damuwar jakuwan su nawa wata uku.
