O'Brien ya ba mata umarni ta bar gidan wanki kuma ta yi wahala, inda mata ta kunna leda ta kuma huro gas mace ga ma'auratan.
Bidiyo da wani mai yawan baya ya dauka yana faruwa da Kelley ya dauki spray din daga hannun mace, kuma ya sami numfashi mai zafi a fusace domin matsalarsa.
O'Brien na iya jin rawar makamai a baya, yayin da mai bata wannan suna yayo tare da ɗan karensu.
O'Brien ta raba bidiyon a Facebook kuma ta ce wa ABC 10 cewa yana so yin girmamawa "ta je gidan yari."
Fasfofi sun zama wajibi a duk fadin jihar California, ko a cikin sabulu mai kyau.
Kwamfutarka suna da iko ya zama kwamfutar 'yan sanda aka kamala, ciki har da lokacin cin abinci ko sha ruwa.
Duk da haka, babu wani inda a shari'ar cutar korona na jihar da ke cewa cewa masu kallo zasu iya amfani da makamai da ba su kashe ba don hukunta wannan tsarin.
Ko a yanzu, a cikin lokacin da ake "yin watsi da masu sauraro", hakan bai hana zuwa a kan laifi mai karfin dakatar da mutum ta hanyar haraji ne da dama na $1,000 ko kuma zuwa shekaru uku a cikin gidan kurkuku na jihar.
Scotland-England Union Chain Kofa ɗiɗa ce da shekaru 200
Titi mai hada Skotland da Ingila ya yi shekaru 200 kafin a ayyana rajista na £10m na gyaruwa.
Tashar Lantarki ta Union Chain Bridge ta kwarewa Mai Rabin Tweed daga Fishwick a kan Scottish Borders zuwa Horncliffe a Northumberland.
Da ya buɗe a shekara ta 1820, shi ne kwararren titi mai ɗaukin dan h̟alik̟a a duniya mai tsawon 449ft (137m).
Ya kasance kuma titin mota na farko na irin sa a Birtaniya.
Tashar Jirgin tsaro ta yi amfani da hannu Mai Bauta Samuel Brown na ƙasarm Ingila.
Ya sami damar fitar da kuma samar da tsarin ɓarna wato 'iron chains' bayan da rashin jituwa na Jami'an Nafawa ta ƙasa sa shi mai ya manta da kwarorrukan jahar ragewa daga taliyoyin.
Abokan Hulda na Union Chain Bridge da kuma Jami'ar Muhalli Civil Engineers (Ice) Scotland suna shaida shekaru dubu biyu da hidimar daidaituwar wani sabon lambu.
Robert Hunter, daga cikin kungiyar abokan aiki, ya ce: "Wannan kira ne a gaskiya a garesu na cewa wata daga cikin kowanne babban titi a duniya da kuma kyakkyawar ingantacciya a fannin injiniyanci."
Mun shirya tarurrukan yawa domin yiwuwar wannan lokaci, amma ba daidai ba sai suka dakatar da su.
Duk da haka, gaskiyar cewa aikin zama ya yi kusa da farawa akan gyara ɗin da aka sanar da kudin £10m shine kyakkyawar hadiyar ranar haihuwa da za'a samu kuma hakan zai tabbata jerin shekarun da za su zo su sule gurin daga nan baya za su iya sha'awar titin dukkanin siffar shi.
Ma'aikacin Ice Scotland Hannah Smith ya bayyana kwarin gwiwar matsakaichi na Scotland da cewa ita ce "wani bangare na almara mai fesfcar hali" na daular ilmantar engineering na Scotland.
Ta ce: "Mun sani cewa duniya bata jin dadinsa kuma ya yi kyau cewa aikin gyara zai fara da wuri nan take."
Girgizar Salmonella ya harbi mutane 212 a jihohi 23
25 ga Yuli (UPI) -- Babban Makarantar Kula da Cututtuka ta Amurka ke bincike kan wani taron cutar Salmonella da ya sha aiki wa mutane 212 a jihohi 23 na kasar.
A sanarwa ta Juma'a daga CDC sun ruwaito cewa mutane 87 sun kamu da cuta tun daga sabuwar bayanin da ya gabatar a ranar Talata.
Hukumar ta ce mutane suka fara nuna alamun da ke da alaƙa da wani nau'in salmonella, wanda zai iya daukar kwana biyu zuwa hudu don bayyana alamun, tsakanin 19 ga Yuni da 11 ga Yuli.
Talatin da daya mutane sun kai asibiti tun daga lokacin da cutar ta faru, amma babu wanda ya sha mutuwa daga cikin su.
Bayanin CDC, wani tushe mai tsari na da'idin Salmonella bai bayyana ba.
Bai fitar da wani shawarwari kan ci ko sha abubuwan abinci ba, ko sanya sunan gidajen adireshin da ke sayar da kayayyakin da suka dauki kwaro ba.
Oregon ya yi mummunan yawa na cutar salmonella, da yawan cututtuka 51, hakanan Utah ya biyu da 'yan'uwansa da yawan cututtuka 40 da aka ruwaito.
Salmonella shine cutar bakteriya ce, wadda ta haifar da cututtuka 1.35 miliyan, damuwa 26,500 ciki jami'a, da rassa 420 kowane shekara, a bisa (CDC).
Mafi yawancin alamun cutar Salmonella sune ciwon yantsi, zazzabi, da rikicin ciki, wadanda za su fara ne tsakanin awanni shida da kwanaki shida bayan haskeh.
Cutar ta yiwuwa ta kasance tsawon rana hudu zuwa bakwai, kuma mutane mafi yawa su samu warwarewa ba tare da magani ba, amma wasu kuma su bukaci kiwon asibiti.
Makiyaya: Man United, Chelsea shiga CL; Bournemouth, Watford juya daga EPL
Manchester United da Chelsea sun shiga gasar cin kofin Shiga gasar kwallon kafa ta nahiyar Turai a saboda Leicester a ranar karshe na kakar gasar Firimiya ta Lahadi, yayin da Bournemouth da Watford suka fuskanci raguwa domin kare shekara biyar a cikin teburin kwallon kafa na farfajiyar.
United ta ci 2-0 a kan Leicester ta hanyar kwallaye daga Bruno Fernandes da Jesse Lingard domin bayarwa kungiyar Ole Gunnar Solskjaer matsayin na uku.
Chelsea ta doke Wolverhampton 2-0 bayan kwallon da taimako daga Mason Mount sannan ta kammala a wurin na hudu da karshe na tsakanin gasar Champions ta duniya a kan Leicester, wanda yake cikin huduwar gasar na farko a kusan karshen kakar da jiki.
Leicester, maimakon haka, zasu buga wasan gasar Europa tare da Tottenham, wanda ya kammala magana 1-1 a kan Crystal Palace domin samun wurin na shida - sama da Wolverhampton akan bambancin kwallaye.
Yakin ƙaryar ɗaukacin relegation guda biyu, ya koma ƙarshen matsalar ne yadda Aston Villa sakaɓa a minti na 84, suka ƙaryata a minti daya daga nan, sai suka jagoranta wajen zaɓe ƙarara 1-1 a West Ham don suka subsist.
Kwamandan Jack Grealish ya ci kwallon Villa a wani gasar da zai iya kasancewa na ƙarshe ga ɗan kungiyar da ya yi sallah daga yaro.
Bournemouth ya yi abin da yake bukatar ya yi kuma ya yenke da Everton, 3-1, amma ya kare ɗaya ne kasa Villa.
Watford din ya faduwa ne kuma a matsayin kungiyar da ta gaban karshe bayan da ta rasa 3-2 a hannun Arsenal.
Manchester City ya wuce 100 golewa na tallafawa da cin kwallon 5-0 akan Norwich mai ƙarshe a'a wurin kungiyoyin wasan kwallon ƙafa na Premier League, wata ƙarshen wani ɗan wasa shi ne David Silva bayan shekara 10 tare da Manchester City.
Kevin De Bruyne ya samu kulawa na ɗaya ta 20 da ya hadu kamar tarihin gasar, kuma ya yi nasara sau biyu.
Liverpool ya gama wannan kakar da ke fadada shi a matsayin mai lashe shi da ci 3-1 a kan Newcastle kuma ya kammala da dama mara misaltuwa na 99.
