Kanye West ya yi wa matarsa Kim Kardashian yabo a gaban al'umma bayan binciken aure
Kanye West ya yi wa matarsa Kim Kardashian hakuri don gabatar da "batun sirri" a jama'a.
Mawakin yace a wani taron da aka yi a Kudancin Carolina cewa kwanciyar kuwa suka yi tunanin kunne shi wanda ke karkashin gabatarwa.
Bayan makon da ya yi tsaka-tsaki, inda ya yi wasu bayanai game da matarsa da 'yan'uwan ta, West ya yi rubutu a shafinsa na Twitter na juyawa.
Yamma ma ya bayyana cewa ya ziyarci asibiti kwanan dawowarsa bayan Justin Bieber ya ziyarta a kauyinsa ta Wyoming.
Ya ce: "Ina so in yi wa matata Kim yabo bisa abun da ya faru tsakaninmu wanda ya kamata ya kasance al'amari na kusa da mu."
Ban taba ta daka ta kamar yadda ta daka ni ba.
"Ga Kim, ina so in fada in sanar da kai cewa na ji na baka rauni. Don Allah yi min gafara. Na gode maka domin kullum kasancewa nan domin ni."
Sako masu rashin daidaituwa na West, wanda ke dauke da bayanin cewa matarsa ta koka shafi mai suna kula da shi tare da yiwa Uwar shi, Kris Jenner.
Ya kuma ce ya yi ƙoƙari ya rabu da Kardashian West, wanda ya aure a shekarar 2014.
Tsakanin damuwa game da yanayin tunanin mijinta, Kardashian West, mahaifiyar 'ya'yanshi hudu na West, ta fitar da sanarwar mai tsawo wajen cewa ita da 'yan'uwanta "sun samu damuwa" wajen shiga tsakanin su, kuma ta yi wa wasu 'yan talaka damu cewa ya da matsalar tafari-dum-dum.
Ta ce: "Shi ne mutum mai ban mamaki amma mai sauũi, wanda a kan laifukan yin matakin maĩyara da kuma mutum daƙin mai launi, wanda ya sha dukaƙuƙen rasuwar uwar sa, kuma ya dawo da gurbatawar gurbatawa da gurbatawa da ke ƙarin bayarwar ciwon yau da kullum. yana maganin ciwon hali mai tasowa."
Ta ƙara cewa ba ta yi hirar lafiyarsa ba tare da shi ba saboda "ina da kadan kai ga 'ya'ya namu da bakin kaso na Kanye kan lafiyarsa."
Ta kara da cewa: "Amma yau, na ji kamar yana da kyau muyi magana akan wannan saboda damuwa da matsalolin tunanin lafiya."
Yammacin ya bayyana sunayensa na garkuwa ne a wani taro a ranar 19 ga watan Yuli.
Yankin Isra'ila yawan masu cutar coronavirus ya wuce 60,000 saboda karuwar cututtuka
JERUSALEM (Reuters) - Lambobin mutane da suka sami nasarar gwaji mai kyau na korona bangaren virus a Isra'ila na sama da 60,000 a Asabar da zamu, yayin da gwamnatin ke kula dasu kawaici da farga don katakar dawo da cutar.
Sabbin bayanan rana ta gobe suka nuna 1,770 sabbin cututtuka, wanda ya kai jumlar yawan laifuka zuwa 60,496, hukumar lafiya ta ƙasar ta ruwaito.
Da mutane takwas da suka kai miliyan biyu, Isra'ila ta ruwaito cikakken kudade 455 daga cutar annobar.
Isra'ila itace daga cikin kasashen farko da suka umurci daukar hankalin shugaban kasa a kasa, kuma a kan farko ta samu nasara a rufe sanadin kai tsaye kan cutar.
Yawan yau da kullun da ya kasance dari suka ragu zuwa sakamakon lambobi guda ɗayaɗaya.
Mashawarcin kan matsalar arzikin, gwamnatin ya saukake waɗannan makiyayya - da sanyi sosai, wasu hukumomi suka yarda - da dawowar tasa na cutar.
Sabuwar kashe-kashe na badakalar turai-turai na irin wasu masana'antu na tattalin arziki ya mayar da tashin hankali na al'umma, wanda ke haifar da murabus madaidaici a kowace rana.
