"Ko dai a cikin hanyar kasuwa, ko ta waje a cikin haɗin kasa biyu da Spain ko ƙasa ɗaya ta musamman, inda muka ga ya kamata mu sake yin aiki da sauki."
"Maimakon haka, mun gudana dakile-maru zuwa Birtaniya, watakila fashe mai kayatarwa a nan, sannan kuma wata kulle-kasa."
Mai hannu a kan haramtalle na Spaniya tsaro kuma harijaji da karantin da suka tafka
Sauyin zakara ta yi bayan da Sipen ya dauki fiye da dubu 900 na sabuwar yau da kullum Covid-19 ga rana biyu a jere.
Wazirin Ƙasashen Ƙariya ya tabbatar da cewa wasu marubutan suka bar waɽanci ba tare da lokacin soke ko sauya tsarinsu ba.
"Na gane cewa yana damfara wa wadanda ke nunawa wannan abu da ke tukwici ko wadanda ke zargin zuwa, amma ya kamata mu zamo mafarki da ma, mu mallaki mataki mai sauri mai siffa, domin kare Kasar UK," yace.
