"Idan wani ya kasance yana biyan dokar dangane da karantin da kuma kwaf da kansa yadda ya kamata, ba za a iya janye masa sakamako ba."
QB Herbert a cikin 4 zaɓe-zaben da aka sanya a hannun Chargers
